@ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5269
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### Routed to Auth Service (localhost:5003)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dave@example.com",
  "password": "SuperSecret123!"
}

### Also routed to Auth Service
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dave@example.com",
  "password": "SuperSecret123!"
}

### Routed to Event Service (localhost:5049)
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events/search?keyword=eras
Accept: application/json

### Also routed to Event Service — copy a real id from the search above
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Routed to Booking Service (localhost:5290) — copy a real, Available
### ticket id from the search above, and a real token from login above
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/bookings/reserve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "ticketIds": ["00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"]
}

### Also routed to Booking Service
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/queue/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
